Inguma
------

Installation:
=============

MacOS:
- install Homebrew
- brew install gtk+3 libdnet graphviz
- brew install libffi
- brew install https://raw.githubusercontent.com/secdev/scapy/master/.travis/pylibpcap.rb
- export PKG_CONFIG_PATH="/usr/local/opt/libffi/lib/pkgconfig"
- pip install PyGObject scapy psutil

Clone the git or mercurial repository, and run ./ginguma.py.
